Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,畫了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來好漂亮 好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帶斑紋的果凍很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 果凍球也像水滴一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,外公說明年也可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其實夏祭 或者年末年始參拜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想早點做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但這個作業的山…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}沉甸甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,現在明明冒出來這麼多做點心的點子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假居然有這麼多作業和返校日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,確實很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們班明明是3年級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但發生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因為班會而落下很多進度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小零是幾歲開始想做職業棋手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 小學四年級的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等我發覺過來 就只剩下這條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說 我只能做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,日向喜歡外公的店 所以想幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,現在明明看到了想做的事情 就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,卻不能去碰 讓我很煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說我只是想轉移注意力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,從作業的山 考試 應試那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 就算說什麼志願的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒辦法想像成為高中生的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡能不能順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,又要進入不認識的人中間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說不太清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下週六
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,桐山君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 放晴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今天多謝邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.17,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fs54\bord6\c&HC255F3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fsp12\pos(960,92)}深深鞠躬~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一不小心就自然而然的成了這個情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,請盡情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,題目是水的能量和重力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將科部夏天自由研究的集大成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,流水麵線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害 第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快看 小桃 這就是流水麵線哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小桃最喜歡吸麵條了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,敝宅庭院裡的竹林因為要改建所以就伐掉了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不浪費掉 就這樣物盡其用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.60,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs54\bord4\c&H54FFFD&\3c&H3D83F3&\fsp12\pos(844,62)}堆成山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,麵線煮好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,先把第一盆麵線…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 我來介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.36,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fn微软雅黑\fs54\bord6\c&HFEFF6C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fsp12\pos(960,64)}鞠躬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是川本日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 這是妹妹小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是桐山一直在意的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.88,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs54\bord4\c&HA77DF4&\3c&H8B20E7&\fsp12\frz18.75\pos(424.857,538.143)}心\N動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我就盡量放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼可愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是鋼鐵直男的桐山君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也會突入戀愛的大氣層呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦 青澀的青春 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 那個 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,炸蔬菜花了太多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.42,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn方正准圆_GBK\bord4\be3\c&HC3A5FA&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1612,625)}頭\N髮\N亂\N蓬\N蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.42,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn方正准圆_GBK\bord4\be3\c&HFCDCA0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz9.593\pos(388.2,746.4)}渾\N身\N是\N汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 是老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,零君受您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:53.95,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,0)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs54\bord6\c&HC255F3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fsp12\b1\frz5.116\pos(187.2,738.4)}深\N深\N鞠\N躬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,今天謝謝您的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是炸蔬菜 大家都會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這可真是太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快快 這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又自然而然的變麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,臉像紅黏土一樣紅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,臉像氧化鐵的顏色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是中暑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要放了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先從孩子開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,水放小點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,竹筒的傾角也緩一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的眼睛沒能捕捉到麵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,瞳孔都散了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐在苦戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是瞄準 而是等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,炸蔬菜也好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:50.61,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fn方正准圆_GBK\bord4\be3\c&HF7DE86&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz2.694\pos(585.334,320.111)}燃\N燒\N殆\N盡\N感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是飢餓的男生時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大量的上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,中大獎 中大獎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.83,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fn方正准圆_GBK\bord6\be3\c&HC778F5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz352.1\pos(1718.134,452.911)}粉\N\N紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,粉紅的換炸雞一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的是綠色 得到綠色了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,綠色沒中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,請排到末尾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是粉紅耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要去領炸雞塊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒有流過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,粉紅 又來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 讓我也吃點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這些麵全都是我煮的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,炸雞塊好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一碗 一碗份就好 給我流一碗來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老師是沒接住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小零很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 真的很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真好 還有這麼開心的高中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,炸雞 炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(526,1060)}考這裡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276,1060)}我要考這裡試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.93,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\c&H7A6F72&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(1785,1060)}暑 假{\fs42}  ②
Comment: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B-Title==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:47.93,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\c&H814823&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(132,450)}新 的 一 年
Comment: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B-PART=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,過了年進入1月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就要考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這個圖形這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這個啊 畫條輔助線就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,畫在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在最空的地方畫上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對 我決定報小零在的私立駒橋高中為第一志願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣讓他教我學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去橋高 這樣告訴小零的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 橋高？ 日向嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不知為什麼 小零好開心好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我還不知道能不能考上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 也沒有上補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天 他拿著學習計劃來了我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,時間還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始準備 絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,之後每週都有幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家吃過晚餐以後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,開始輔導我學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點抓到竅門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 數學只能多做幾次找到感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆點一道一道做就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小零教得很耐心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也很容易懂 幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,宵夜的預感？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 有人想被慣著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想被慣著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,慣著？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,炸豆腐和天婦羅都加了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是川本家傳說中的 嬌慣烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,煮軟的天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,加上旁邊還有蘸滿湯汁的甜甜的炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃的旁邊還有好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太幸福啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嬌慣烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要炸豆腐 還是天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我選不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為了治癒女兒的煩惱而開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,二者都放的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其名為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嬌慣烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽在我考試時經常給我做宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也決定 日向考試時一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好開心 真的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 再加把油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室還沒停火 最後拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想要去小零讀的私立高中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只是感覺想去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道該不該說這樣的任性話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天開了路邊攤 我才發覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 1個250日元的小小的甜甜的點心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,到底凝聚了多少工夫 時間和金錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,煮豆沙的日子 天還沒亮外公就站在了大鍋前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,留在外公手裡的 一個能有多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而我如果去了私立高中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為此 外公要做多少個點心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 駒橋高中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這個夏天 你們也努力開店了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,從計算成本 做點心賣點心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,直到關店都很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你這麼愛關心人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,外公做這個點心 能剩下多少利潤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你會去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“小孩子不用想那種事情”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,錢很重要 這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,認識到這一點的你很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小看你外公是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人還等著外公的點心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我還要和豆沙餡好好戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個理由就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,外公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的就是你過得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,外公…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是怎麼說呢 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你姐姐查了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那小子去的駒橋高中 偏差值很高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,加油學習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去那個高中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 小零 那個 關於這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在解將軍將棋的小零像被吸進去一樣安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我也被傳染了 很能集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜到不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,打開窗簾 窗戶外面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是今年的第一場雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.96,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\c&H7A6F72&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(1790,1060)}新 的 一 年
